                        <li> <span class="fa-li"><i class="fas fa-check"></i></span>
                          Geothermal monitoring and forecasting </li>
                        <li> <span class="fa-li"><i class="fas fa-check"></i></span>
                          Tailored uncertainty characterisation and propagation
                        </li>
                        <li> <span class="fa-li"><i class="fas fa-check"></i></span>
                          Generalisation of techniques and methods for
